                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "\n                              <p rend=\"align(center)\">Private</p>\n                              <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <date>Dec 6. 1852</date>\n                                        <placeName>New York</placeName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Rev Dr Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">In your note to me in answer<lb/> to a complaining\n                                        one of mine respecting<lb/> the call of\n                                                  <persName>Marcussohn</persName>. You promised<lb/>\n                                        to give room in your Paper &amp;<lb/> any reply I might have\n                                        to make</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">As I have no knowledge of the<lb/> case in its\n                                        origin only through correspondence<lb/> I shall let\n                                        correspondents reply to<lb/>\n                                        <persName>Mr <sic>Marcussohns</sic></persName> letter of\n                                                  <date>Sept 16<lb/> 1852</date> in the Occident. I\n                                        have an addition<lb/>al letter upon the same subject by<lb/>\n                                        <persName>Rev Mr Davis</persName> who wrote the letter<lb/>\n                                        respecting his (<persName>Mr M</persName>) conversion<lb/>\n                                        in Jewish Chronicle <date>Aug.</date> No.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">By inserting <persName>Rev C. D.\n                                                  Oliver's</persName> letter<lb/> here enclosed, you\n                                        will do justice to the<lb/> clergymen of\n                                                  <placeName>Montgomery Ala.</placeName> who<lb/>\n                                        supposed <persName>Mr Marcussohn</persName> sincere<lb/> in\n                                        his professions. I would beg you<lb/> also to insert the few\n                                        remarks I have<lb/> sent you enclosed, which may<lb/> serve\n                                        to show how far <persName>Mr M.</persName> carried<lb/> the\n                                        deception either of himself or of others</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(5)\">Yours with great respect</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(5)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">E R McGregor</persName>\n                              </p>\n                    </body>\n          </text>\n</TEI>\n"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3bc3th34/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
